@Fohlen it looks like your mutation is query is wrong. It should be:

```
mutation ($email: String!) {
   create_invitation(email: $email) {
       invitation {
           creation_date
      }
   }
}
```

Notice that the argument to the mutation comes first and then the variable you are passing to the mutation: `create_invitation(email: $email)`

Did you construct the mutation in the GraphiQL browser or just by hand?

